s. african trade surplu rise sharpli in februari south africa 's trade surplu rose to 1.62 billion rand in februari after fall to 906.2 mln in januari , custom and excis figur show . thi compar with a year earlier surplu of 958.9 mln rand . export rose slightli to 3.36 billion rand in februari from 3.31 billion in januari but import fell to 1.74 billion from 2.41 billion . thi brought total export for the first two month of 1987 to 6.67 billion rand and import to 4.15 billion for a total surplu of 2.52 billion rand against 1.71 billion a year earlier .